page.title: 20Appendix.
page.content:
Whilst every attempt has been made to ensure the information contained in this survey is as accurate as possible there are a couple qualificatios to be made:- 1.The information relating to the number of doctor and dentist practices' in the area may not be entirely accurate.The number is probably more than those recorded.
2.The survey does not contain information relating to"alternative medicine'practices in the area.
3.The number of post boxes and telephone booths are not listed.
M.Clements.
